      <title>据称阿曼 OQ 计划通过勘探部门 IPO 筹集 20 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/oman-s-oq-to-sell-25-stake-in-exploration-unit-s-landmark-ipo</link>
